{"tid":1850972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡狗屋被高溫消毒","createTime":"2020-01-29T22:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T01:20:43.000Z","uid":125168,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a033d556ecf545bd82d95974fe498cf9fae1f1f3","tid":1850972,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T22:54:16.000Z","msg":"紅磡警署遭三黑衣人投擲汽油彈縱火<br />\n18分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】紅磡警署凌晨被人投擲汽油彈縱火，無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警署外牆及行人路被熏黑，地下留有玻璃樽碎片，便衣警員在現場檢走碎片調查。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨二時許，三名身穿黑色衣物的男子，向紅磡警署車場出入口位置投擲數枚汽油彈之後逃去，事件中無人受傷、毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n警員在附近一帶兜截，暫時未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"ac30e8778ce0fca7533c9fce793dcce75fcfc788","tid":1850972,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T22:56:31.000Z","msg":"真正嘅靜靜地"},{"pid":"a293d4e9869697ca1eb0bcba2dcf5fdbc1cb2709","tid":1850972,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T22:58:08.000Z","msg":"原來何文田狗屋都消咗毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48ca2dd719f07a02edd2e32abb2c1c6a26babd2","tid":1850972,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T22:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d1dcd0a68b0f38580058300f9fc86472d36259","tid":1850972,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T23:00:01.000Z","msg":"仲未有狗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f05f203b26ca652ba0cb947d12bb8bcd565721","tid":1850972,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T23:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87105ae2e6872332357ce7d70492d87059b4db6a","tid":1850972,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,